column1: Baby Barnaby's////The green eggs are two scrabbled eggs made with artichokes
column2: cheese and maybe one other thing and it's delicious. It comes with a side of chicken sausage
column4: potatoes and toast. The potatoes were cut in little cubes and crunchy. Just dip them in ketchup and you're good to go. My BF and I subbed the toast for a biscuit. BEST. DECISION. EVER. And it comes with two biscuits!! The biscuits are so fluffy with a hint of sweet. Amazing. We thoroughly enjoyed our meals and will return!
